txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Enlarged carapaces from the insects surrounding Tyrn Lhuig. Delivery of the items should be made to Othran at the base of the hilltop outpost.
'Carapaces can be used to reinforce buildings and armour. We will take whatever you collect, if you choose.'
Council of the North Task: Enlarged Carapaces
The hunters at Tyrn Lhuig expect a delivery of enlarged carapaces to be made to Othran, one of their number at the bottom of their hillside outpost.
Deliver the enlarged carapaces to Othran at Tyrn Lhuig in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver enlarged carapaces from the insects surrounding Tyrn Lhuig to Othran at the bottom of the hillside outpost.
Wanted: Enlarged carapaces from the insects surrounding Tyrn Lhuig.
